{"tid":944885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"署任白宮幕僚長　曾形容特朗普「糟糕」","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T12:50:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10729ac493d6ef548ca73a99d7a981e07400514c","tid":944885,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181217/20570438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570438&d=4fxo2yBMJBQe44kZOiiPxAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=13892a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570438&h=0ef9d5c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181217/20570438</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月17日 <br />\n<br />\n署任白宮幕僚長　曾形容特朗普「糟糕」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181217/large/a1806a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181217%2Flarge%2Fa1806a.gif&h=591585e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬爾瓦尼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮行政管理和預算辦公室主任將馬爾瓦尼（Mick Mulvaney）獲任命署任白宮幕僚長後，隨即被翻舊賬。有美媒上載一段前年他角逐連任眾議員時跟民主黨對手辯論時的影片，當中他形容總統特朗普是「糟糕的人類」，不是孩子的榜樣，他支持特朗普，只因其對手希拉莉更為差勁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「美國史上最差的人」<br />\n<br />\n「我喜歡特朗普嗎？不。我們或許有美國史上最差的人類競選總統。」他在片中指為了選民，「用盡所有熱情支持特朗普」。馬爾瓦尼發言人回應指影片是「舊聞」，「馬爾瓦尼在任期內對總統的支持從未動搖，他尊重總統，亦喜歡為他工作」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，「特朗普熊啤啤」成為美國人聖誕另類送禮佳品。頭頂半禿金髮、紅領帶、星星條紋披肩，讓熊公仔成為共和民主兩黨的搶手貨，前者用作歌頌總統，後者用作嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n「喜歡和憎恨特朗普的人都會買，熊公仔像是人們發洩情緒的避雷針。」製造商副主席布拉克特指，熊公仔代表特朗普信奉的價值。不過不少零售商拒絕入貨，亦有電視台不肯播它的廣告，因其政治性太強。布拉克特指公司持續收到很多恐嚇信，已報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美內政部長辭任　稱遭「殘暴政治攻擊」"},{"pid":"b4524616d14328729a72ef91bedc7d2fd3928431","tid":944885,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2018/11/12/15/trumpy-bear.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F15%2Ftrumpy-bear.png&h=b42b8cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec6f8cf52d8a8f4908d4e4a988929d000f3ed733","tid":944885,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4524616d14328729a72ef91bedc7d2fd3928431","tid":944885,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2018/11/12/15/trumpy-bear.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F15%2Ftrumpy-bear.png&h=b42b8cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc4b275b93cad6875b4fdc4ab5732e16134d2be","tid":944885,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"侵仔日日新鮮"}]}